# Google OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs & Services → Credentials
# 2. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 3. Add your app URL to "Authorised JavaScript origins" (e.g. http://localhost:5173)
# 4. Enable "Google Sheets API" under APIs & Services → Library
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_oauth_client_id_here

# 同步試算表名稱（VITE_SHEET_NAME）不放在這裡——
# 由已提交的 .env.development / .env.staging（測試表）與 .env.production（正式表）依 build mode 決定，
# 詳見 docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-09-git-branch-workflow-design.md
